WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN

VALUES (i.[CreationTime], i.[CreatorUserId], i.[DamageCompensationId], i.[DosyaActive], i.[DosyaAdi], i.[DosyaTyp], i.[DosyaUzantisi], i.[DosyaYolu], i.[LastModificationTime], i.[LastModifierUserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted3;

INNER JOIN @inserted3 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

(@p68, @p69, @p70, @p71, @p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, 2),
(@p78, @p79, @p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, 3)) AS i ([CreationTime], [CreatorUserId], [DamageCompensationId], [DosyaActive], [DosyaAdi], [DosyaTyp], [DosyaUzantisi], [DosyaYolu], [LastModificationTime], [LastModifierUserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([CreationTime], [CreatorUserId], [DamageCompensationId], [DosyaActive], [DosyaAdi], [DosyaTyp], [DosyaUzantisi], [DosyaYolu], [LastModificationTime], [LastModifierUserId])
VALUES (i.[CreationTime], i.[CreatorUserId], i.[DamageCompensationId], i.[DosyaActive], i.[DosyaAdi], i.[DosyaTyp], i.[DosyaUzantisi], i.[DosyaYolu], i.[LastModificationTime], i.[LastModifierUserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted3;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [DamageCompensationsFileInfos] t
INNER JOIN @inserted3 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

MERGE [AbpAuditLogs] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, 0),

WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([BrowserInfo], [ClientIpAddress], [ClientName], [CustomData], [Exception], [ExceptionMessage], [ExecutionDuration], [ExecutionTime], [ImpersonatorTenantId], [ImpersonatorUserId], [MethodName], [Parameters], [ReturnValue], [ServiceName], [TenantId], [UserId])
VALUES (i.[BrowserInfo], i.[ClientIpAddress], i.[ClientName], i.[CustomData], i.[Exception], i.[ExceptionMessage], i.[ExecutionDuration], i.[ExecutionTime], i.[ImpersonatorTenantId], i.[ImpersonatorUserId], i.[MethodName], i.[Parameters], i.[ReturnValue], i.[ServiceName], i.[TenantId], i.[UserId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [AbpAuditLogs] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

(@p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, @p56, @p57, @p58, @p59, @p60, @p61, 2)) AS i ([CreationTime], [CreatorUserId], [DamageCompensationId], [DosyaActive], [DosyaAdi], [DosyaTyp], [DosyaUzantisi], [DosyaYolu], [LastModificationTime], [LastModifierUserId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN

VALUES (i.[CreationTime], i.[CreatorUserId], i.[DamageCompensationId], i.[DosyaActive], i.[DosyaAdi], i.[DosyaTyp], i.[DosyaUzantisi], i.[DosyaYolu], i.[LastModificationTime], i.[LastModifierUserId])

INTO @inserted2;

FROM [AbpAuditLogs]
WHERE @@ROWCOUNT = 1 AND [Id] = scope_identity();
